description: Kyle Quinn is looking to buff up a little at his local gym. Not that he's out of shape, he just wants to work on certain areas of his physique. Or at least that's his excuse. Truth be told, the physique he really wants to focus on belongs to Jeremy Bilding, the trainer at the gym. So when Jeremy has him go through some reps on the bench, it becomes obvious very quickly what kind of workout Kyle is really interested in. Enjoy!
title: RAISING THE BAR
